title: ISic020305. ISic020305
body:
Facsimile Images

«ḥΑΛΕΝΙΑΙ»

Apparatus criticus

Text after Agostiniani 1977 (IAS I)

English translation

Italian translation

commentary

The inscription was scratched over a previous text (probably an Attic abbreviation, see Hackl 1909, pp. 39-40, XLVI), partly overlapping it.
